snippet.title: Death by AI | OFFICIAL RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Play now for FREE! on itch.io: https://bobbodev.itch.io/death-by-ai

Or at our site: https://deathbyai.gg

Please report any bugs or talk about the game or just come and say hi here! https://discord.com/invite/BBT45agDyc

Death by AI is a Jackbox like party game for up to 8 players. you can play on any device!
